       01  JANELA-PROGRAMA                PIC X(10).

           COPY "MAINRTN.MSG".
           COPY "ACUGUI.DEF".

       SCREEN SECTION.
       01  TELA-PRINCIPAL.
           03 LABEL       LINE 01,5 COL 03
